### ğŸ”¹ Topics:

| Concept                   | Why Itâ€™s Important                    | Example in Unity                                   |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Classes & Inheritance** | Reuse logic, extend functionality     | `Enemy` inherits from `Character`                  |
| **Interfaces**            | Define common behavior                | `IDamageable` for all objects that can take damage |
| **Events & Delegates**    | Decouple systems (UI, gameplay)       | Health system triggers UI update                   |
| **Coroutines**            | Delay actions, timers, smooth effects | Reload gun after 2 seconds                         |
| **Generics**              | Reusable, type-safe systems           | Generic object pool manager                        |
| **LINQ**                  | Clean, powerful data handling         | Sort or filter enemies list                        |
| **Enums & Structs**       | Manage states or data groups          | PlayerState enum: Idle, Run, Jump                  |

